<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>&#8230;we're not asking you to believe this story. Indeed, skepticism is a sign of a healthy mind. All of us were like you once, with all our biases and science and religions/lack thereof. You may keep your preconceived notions, for now.</em></p>
<p><em>All we ask is that you remember what you have read here. And when your time comes, when you close your eyes in this world and open them to three moons in a sky of green, you will remember who your guardian angels are &#8212; and join us.</em></p>
<h2 id="toc0"><span>You are watched. You are protected. You are loved.</span></h2>
<h2 id="toc1"><span>☽☽☽</span></h2>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><em>&#8212; excerpt from a ☽☽☽ Initiative recruitment tract collected in Baltimore, MD</em></p>
</div>
<br />
<script type="text/javascript" src="http://d3g0gp89917ko0.cloudfront.net/v--3e3a6f7dbcc9/common--javascript/yahooui/tabview-min.js">
